CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper September 27, 1958, pg. 28, reads: "Riding in Style - Thousands of Pittsburghers formed a cheering throng of humanity on Downtown streets Monday afternoon as the second-place Pittsburgh Pirates were honored with a mammoth parade... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Convertible in parade honoring Pittsburgh Pirates, with baseball players Bill Mazeroski and Ron Blackburn seated on back, in front of People's First National Bank, Downtown
